.row.footer-boxes
  .span4
    %h2 The PetHomeStay Way
    %p
      PetHomeStay is an Australian & New Zealand community, that allows pet owners to easily find local friendly homestays or sitters for their pet. 
      %br
      %br
      Simply register your pet, and search for friendly local people near you. It’s fun, easy & totally free to use.
    = link_to "Discover more", what_is_path, class: 'btn'
  .span4
    %h2 PetHomeStay News
    %p
      Whats all this Beta stuff then?
      %br
      %br
      PetHomeStay is being initially released as a beta site. This means that while we have completed a lot of the main features of the site, it is still a bit of a baby, and there still may be a couple of things that don’t look so flash...
    = link_to "Read more", 'http://pethomestay.wordpress.com/2012/07/24/whats-all-this-beta-stuff-then-2/', class: 'btn'
  - if current_user && current_user.homestay.blank?
    .span4
      %h2 Start a PetHomeStay
      %p 
        Start earning money doing what you love: spending time with awesome animals. All from the comfort of your own home!
        %br
        %br
        Just give us some basic details and we'll create an awesome listings page for you.
      = link_to "Start a PetHomeStay listing", new_homestay_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'
  - elsif current_user
    .span4
      %h2 Update your listing
      %p Want to add more information to your awesome PetHomeStay profile? More info means more enquiries!
      = link_to "Update PetHomeStay listing", edit_homestay_path(current_user.homestay), class: 'btn'
  - else
    .span4
      %h2 Love pets?
      %p If you just love looking after animals then you can be a PetHomeStay service provider. From professional dog kennels and daycare, to casual walkers or overnight stays at your place, you can earn money doing what you love!
      = link_to 'Get started today', new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary"
